        text: `I thank the Minister of State for the response. I would like to ask, how frequent are these sessions? And given that there has been quite a fair bit of discussions on new careers, such as in AI, how are we working together with the teachers to keep them abreast of these developments so that they can then support the students in selecting careers for the future? Ms See Jinli Jean (Nominated Member)`,
