        speaker: `Mr Pritam Singh (Aljunied)`,
        text: `Chair, the first tranche of public funds was disbursed to SPH Media Trust in March 2023. Over four Ministerial Statements in this House, the Government has put out its reasons for making the taxpayers subsidise the running of SPH Media Trust or at least, partly subsidising the running of SPH Media Trust. Mr Pritam Singh (Aljunied) What we have been told is that public funding is needed for three reasons. First, without public funding, SPH Media Trust's transformation into a digital news company will not be able to afford the investment and costs of running its professional newsrooms, which is `,
