        text: `Order. End of Question Time. Clarification by Minister Josephine Teo. Mr Speaker [Pursuant to Standing Order No 22(3), Written Answers to Question Nos 29-32, 41-60, 63-68, 70-84, 86-90, 92-106 and 108 on the Order Paper are reproduced in the Appendix. Question Nos 27-28, 33-40, 61-62, 69, 85, 91, and 107 have been postponed to the sitting of Parliament on 6 October 2020.]`,
