        speaker: `Mr Saktiandi Supaat (Bishan-Toa Payoh)`,
        text: `If there was one buzz word that has been hogging the news, it is the efforts of our Government to go digital. We went from transport to financial sector, then down to the grassroots from buying groceries to buying food at the hawker centres and wet markets, and we have also been pushing very hard to get everyone on board. Mr Saktiandi Supaat (Bishan-Toa Payoh) Since the last Budget, the Government has also launched SMEs Go Digital to help them build stronger digital capabilities so as to secure growth in the digital economy. The aim is to enhance productivity through tools, such as digital ord`,
